              p Join Sony Ambassador and local portrait and wedding photographer Will Stedman for this 60-minute session as he demonstrates how you can shoot some fantastic portrait shots, using basic lighting principles including 5-point lighting.
              p
                | Based in the studio at Park Cameras, this is a great opportunity to learn how you can enhance your photography skills, under the guidance of an experienced photographeralong with seeing the new 
                a(href='https://www.parkcameras.com/p/7014843K', target='_blank', title='Sony a9')  Sony a9
                |  in action.
              p.pc-spacer-xl Will is a wedding, lifestyle and commercial photographer based locally in Guilford, Surrey. Amongst shooting a range of weddings at a wide variety of locations, he has also worked for companies including Wagammama, Talkback Thames and Freemantle media photographing adverts, headshots and more.
              a.pc-btn-standard(href='#', title='') Book Now

            .pc-column.pc-col2
