                br
                |with Jon Bentley
              h3 10:40 - 11:40 | 14:55 - 15:55
              p Join The Gadget Show's Jon Bentley and Amateur Photographer magazine Group Editor Nigel Atherton at Park Cameras in Burgess Hill, as they talk cameras and photography, combining their vast knowledge built up over the many years working with technology and from with the world’s oldest consumer weekly photographic magazine (first published in October 1884!).
              p.pc-spacer-xl During this 60-minute session Jon and Nigel will be accepting questions from the audience.
